        {
            "title": "英偉達轉向實體AI引發亞洲供應鏈全面上漲",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UqMB7qy5P3qOeufFiybcbQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEE141FU_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong> 根據彭博社報導,英偉達公司(Nvidia Corp.)戰略性擴展至「實體AI」領域,正推動其亞洲合作夥伴大幅上漲,該地區在這家晶片巨頭的生產生態系統中日益重要。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">亞洲供應商目前佔英偉達生產成本的約90%,較去年的約65%大幅增加。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一轉變突顯出該公司從純半導體領域向機器人、自主系統和AI賦能製造的轉型,執行長黃仁勳將此描述為人工智慧的下一波重大浪潮。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場對這家科技公司擴張的反應迅速,多家區域企業在合作消息公布後錄得雙位數漲幅。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-54deaaa3-c80d-3467-b1c7-cb8fb8e0fc6c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">LG電子(<span><span>LG Electronics</span></span> Inc.)股價在傳出將家用機器人整合至英偉達平台的消息後,一度飆升15%,而中國台灣的南亞科技(Nanya Technology Corp.)則在合作消息公布後上漲10%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在中國,惠州德賽西威汽車電子(Huizhou Desay SV Automotive Co.)和博泰車聯網科技(Pateo Connect Technology Shanghai Corp.)在推出智能駕駛解決方案並宣布與這家美國晶片設計商合作後,股價也大幅飆升。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>超大規模雲端業者支出推動北亞科技股持續跑贏大盤</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這股勢頭得到美國「超大規模雲端業者」大規模資本支出的支持,亞馬遜、微軟和Alphabet今年各自承諾投入近2000億美元用於AI支出。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博數據顯示,英偉達佔微軟資本支出的近一半,佔亞馬遜的四分之一,為鴻海等製造商和SK海力士等記憶體專業廠商創造了巨大的連鎖效應。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師認為,需求的擴大使更多硬體供應商能夠進入這個生態系統,科技股比重較高的北亞市場可能會繼續跑贏大盤。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">激增的需求已經在這些合作夥伴的財務業績中顯現。三星半導體部門最近公布利潤增長48倍,而SK海力士的季度盈利則增長了五倍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著AI建設從數位生成演進至現實世界部署,亞洲在先進硬體和機器人領域的成熟基礎設施,為實施實體AI浪潮提供了結構性的重要優勢。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
