        {
            "title": "日本財務大臣片山在黃金週期間對疑似外匯干預保持沉默",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/fdBK3DNNKcX1.O451imqlQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEB6D11U_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong> 日本財務大臣片山皐月週日拒絕就當局上週是否干預以支撐日圓發表評論,此前有報導稱官員自2024年以來首次進入市場。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">片山在烏茲別克斯坦撒馬爾罕對記者表示,她\"現階段不便發表評論\",但她承認\"投機性走勢已持續一段時間\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博社首次報導,財務大臣的這番言論發表之際,正值日圓在週四大幅走強之後,此前當天稍早曾觸及1美元兌160.72日圓的低點。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-93cdc09c-f6e2-345d-bb9a-5bb6e6fa6d2d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博社對央行賬戶的分析顯示,日本當局可能在此次行動中動用了約345億美元。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管存在疑似干預行動,片山提醒市場\"黃金週\"假期仍在進行中,這段時期通常交易量清淡,更容易出現突然的價格波動。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>政策僵局迫近,市場為進一步波動做好準備</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">疑似干預行動發生前,片山和高級貨幣官員三村淳曾就過度外匯波動向交易員發出嚴厲警告。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週四晚間公佈的官方數據證實,日本截至4月27日尚未進入外匯市場,這留下了一個月的空窗期,下一次官方數據發佈將披露當局是否在該月下半月採取了行動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">片山和日本央行副行長氷野龍三目前正在出席地區會議,包括亞洲開發銀行年會。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著政策制定者保持\"不予置評\"的立場,焦點轉向財務省是否會在黃金週假期於週三結束前採取額外措施。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者保持高度警惕,因為對於疑似支出的345億美元缺乏透明度,繼續在全球貨幣交易台引發不確定性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%B2%A1%E5%8B%99%E5%A4%A7%E8%87%A3%E7%89%87%E5%B1%B1%E5%9C%A8%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E9%80%B1%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E5%B0%8D%E7%96%91%E4%BC%BC%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AF%E5%B9%B2%E9%A0%90%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E6%B2%89%E9%BB%98-024733510.html",
